An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing. The alien may have acted differently, it has been proposed, if it was aware of this great difficulty. 
In the end, this is probably a good thing.
 The more the alien knew of our cruel species, the less it might feel friendly. This would not suit the ultimate purpose of the alien, which was to learn and hopefully assist humankind. Matt Damon picks this up quickly when "kidnapped", and works with the alien to try and communicate with one another. The alien is actually a benevolent being that has traveled from the far future, and Matt Damon was a convenient, well-rounded choice for it;

